## The 6 roles and what they do

| Role | Pipeline responsibility | Directus role name |
|---|---|---|
| **Owner** | God mode — sees everything, can toggle other roles' capabilities | `Administrator` (Directus built-in) |
| **Admin** | Sales/admin — creates orders, manages customers & products, finalises, handles returns | Custom role `Admin` |
| **Warehouse** | Cold storage weighing, packing | Custom role `Warehouse` |
| **Production** | Cutting instructions | Custom role `Production` |
| **Finance** | Payment approval gate | Custom role `Finance` |
| **Courier** | Dispatch & delivery, proof photos, GPS | Custom role `Courier` |

> **Important:** The **Owner** maps to Directus's built-in **`Administrator`** role — that one already has full access to everything, you don't configure it. You only need to create + configure the **other 5 custom roles**.

---

## Role 1 — Owner (Directus `Administrator`)

**Nothing to do.** Directus's built-in Administrator role has full CRUD on every collection and every field. Just assign the owner user to this role.

